@startuml
title 点赞/取消点赞评论时序图

actor 用户 as User
participant "CommentController" as Ctrl
participant "CommentService" as Svc
participant "CommentMapper" as Mapper
database "MySQL" as DB
database "Redis" as Redis

User -> Ctrl: 点赞/取消点赞请求(commentId, likeStatus)
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> Svc: likeComment(commentId, likeStatus)
activate Svc



Svc -> Svc: 从ThreadLocal获取userId


Svc -> Mapper: selectById(commentId)
activate Mapper
Mapper -> DB: 查询评论
DB --> Mapper: 返回Comment对象
Mapper --> Svc: 返回comment
deactivate Mapper

alt 评论不存在
    Svc --> Ctrl: 返回"评论不存在"
    Ctrl --> User: 返回错误信息
    deactivate Ctrl
    deactivate Svc
end


alt likeStatus == 0 (取消点赞)
    Svc -> Redis: 删除set中的用户id
    activate Redis
    Redis --> Svc: 返回移除结果
    deactivate Redis

    alt 移除失败 (result == null 或 result == 0)
        Svc --> Ctrl: 返回"取消点赞失败"
        Ctrl --> User: 返回错误信息
        deactivate Ctrl
        deactivate Svc
    end

else likeStatus == 1 (点赞)
    Svc -> Redis: 添加用户id至set中
    activate Redis
    Redis --> Svc: 返回添加结果
    deactivate Redis

    alt 添加失败 (result == null 或 result == 0)
        Svc --> Ctrl: 返回"点赞失败"
        Ctrl --> User: 返回错误信息
        deactivate Ctrl
        deactivate Svc
        note right: 流程结束
    end
end



Svc --> Ctrl: 返回成功
Ctrl --> User: 返回成功信息

deactivate Svc
deactivate Ctrl

@enduml
